Interface COM.sootNsmoke.jvm.RuntimeConstants

public interface RuntimeConstants
A collection of handy constants for working with class files. Add this class to the implements clause in your class and you will be able to refer to (for example) the void signature as SIG_VOID. instead of RuntimeConstants.SIG_VOID. This class has no interfaces, so you don't have to worry about implementing any methods.
